<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">Enter the date that the payment should be posted.</td>
</tr>
<tr sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">
