<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">Enter the balance amount while closing. The amount that is indicated in the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">Amount</strong> field in the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">Balance</strong> form is displayed by default.</td>
</tr>
