<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">Select the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">Automatic</strong> check box to create and post a journal that is preset on the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">Accounts payable parameters</strong> page.</td>
</tr>
