<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">Enter the date that the payment should be posted.</td>
</tr>
<tr sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">Amount to be transferred</strong></td>
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">Enter the balance amount while closing. The amount that is indicated in the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">Amount</strong> field in the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">Balance</strong> form is displayed by default.</td>
</tr>
<tr sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">Automatic</strong></td>
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">Select the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">Automatic</strong> check box to create and post automatically a journal that is preset on the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-advance-holders-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">Accounts payable parameters</strong> page.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
